==Description==
The '''Purple Shard''' is a type of [[Underground|Underground Item]] first encountered in [[Johto]].

==Details==
The Purple Shard can be used with [[Quest Points]] {{Questpoints}} to obtain items from [[Shard Trader|Shard Traders]].

==Mine Layout==
The Purple Shard appears in the Underground as a 3x2 sized object.<br><br>
[[File:PurpleShardMine.png|100px]]

==Trades==
Purple Shards can be used in combination with other [[Shards]] to purchase the following items:
